Title : Nusatsum River
Text : The '''Nusatsum River''' is a [[river]] in the [[Bella Coola Valley]] of the [[British Columbia Coast|Central Coast region]] of [[British Columbia]], [[Canada]].  It is a [[tributary]] of the [[Bella Coola River]], flowing northwest to meet that river just upstream of the community of [[Hagensborg]].<ref>[http://apps.gov.bc.ca/pub/bcgnws/names/17868.html BC Names/GeoBC entry "Nusatsum River"]</ref>

"Nusatsum" has been spelled variously as Nootsatsum, Noosatum, and Nutsatsum.<ref>[http://apps.gov.bc.ca/pub/bcgnws/names/17868.html BC Names/GeoBC entry "Nusatsum River"]</ref>

